---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Web Design for Plumbers | FisherDigital"
  description="Professional websites for plumbing businesses across the UK. Get found on Google, win more emergency callouts, and stop losing jobs to competitors with better sites."
  schemaType="niche"
  niche="Plumbers"
  nicheDescription="Professional websites, AI chatbots, and smart automations built specifically for plumbing businesses in the UK."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-light py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="label block mb-4">Web design for plumbers</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight mb-6">
          Your next job is searching<br />
          <span class="text-accent">Google right now.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)] max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          They need a boiler fixed, a leak stopped, or a bathroom fitted. If your website doesn't show up, or looks like it was built in 2012, they'll call someone else. We build plumbing websites that earn the click and land the job.
        </p>
        <a href="/#contact" data-hover
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-accent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-600 hover:bg-accent-hover transition-all shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 hover:shadow-accent/40">
          Book a free call
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain Points -->
  <section class="bg-white py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="label block mb-4">The problem</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight">
          Three things costing you work.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Pain 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-600 mb-3">Invisible on Google</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Someone searches "plumber near me" at 10pm with a burst pipe. Your website is on page 3. They never see it. The job goes to whoever shows up first.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pain 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-600 mb-3">Competitors look more professional</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            The bloke down the road has a proper website with reviews, a booking form, and photos of real work. Yours has a phone number and a clip art logo. Customers pick the one that looks trustworthy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pain 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-600 mb-3">Losing emergency callouts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Emergency work is high value. But those customers decide in seconds. If your site is slow, broken on mobile, or hard to find, they scroll past and call the next plumber in the list.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build -->
  <section class="section-light py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <span class="label block mb-4">What you get</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight mb-12">
          A website that works as hard as you do.
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">Click-to-call and WhatsApp buttons</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">One tap from their phone to your phone. No forms, no friction. Perfect for emergency callouts when speed matters.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">Local SEO built in from day one</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">Google Business Profile setup, location pages for your service areas, and proper schema markup so Google knows you're a plumber in your town.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">Service pages that rank</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">Individual pages for boiler installs, bathroom fitting, emergency repairs, and every other service you offer. Each one optimised to show up when customers search.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">AI chatbot that answers while you're under a sink</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">On the Professional plan, an AI chatbot handles enquiries 24/7. It can quote ballpark prices, book callbacks, and qualify leads before you even pick up the phone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight mb-6">
        See what your site could look like.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        We built a demo plumbing website to show you the standard. No charge, no commitment. Take a look, then let's talk.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-5">
        <a href="/demos/westbury-plumbing/" data-hover
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-accent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-600 hover:bg-accent-hover transition-all shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 hover:shadow-accent/40">
          See a live demo
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/#contact" data-hover
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-500 border border-[var(--color-border-light)] hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-all">
          Book a free call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
